me.aliceq.heatmap

Class HeatMapDataSet<E extends java.lang.Comparable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.aliceq.heatmap.HeatMapDataSet<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Comparable key type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<E,java.lang.Float>>, java.util.Collection<java.util.Map.Entry<E,java.lang.Float>>, java.util.Set<java.util.Map.Entry<E,java.lang.Float>>

    public class HeatMapDataSet<E extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Set<java.util.Map.Entry<E,java.lang.Float>>
    A read-only window into a HeatMap's data set. This class lists the value-pair associations in a sorted, easily iterable order. This instance contains a copy of the HeatMap data so if the original is altered, this instance is not changed.
